{"tid":1801911,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警員涉直播記者身份證　警方：會調查事件","createTime":"2019-12-29T04:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T04:49:49.000Z","uid":73479,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d300b568c64e4977de7c55bb3e2aff65b1e05db3","tid":1801911,"uid":73479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0YBHm2r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0YBHm2r.jpg&h=0a0fed49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【橙訊】有警員昨日在大埔超級城商場截查一名記者時，於直播鏡頭前展示對方身份證。警察公共關係科總警司郭嘉銓承認，警員當時手持記者的身份證，被記者的攝錄機拍下，警員做法有不對，警方會主動調查事件，並配合私隱專員公署的調查工作。<br />\n<br />\n郭嘉銓今日在記者會上說，涉事警員未有停職，會繼續執勤，指警方重視個人私隱，一直要求警員按照相關指引及守則行事。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，最近有警員和記者於示威現場互相指罵，認為有關情況並不應該，希望各界明白警員在暴力衝擊現場，要迅速辨認不同身份，並不容易，加上早前有人搶犯，又指記者不一定身穿反光衣，而身穿反光衣者也不一定是記者，警方會提醒前線警員克制，避免誤會，希望大家互相尊重。"},{"pid":"f6c4c2a3e5a7b442815d51c29cd477754055aeae","tid":1801911,"uid":297569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:39:16.000Z","msg":"今日有集會啊 大家記得要去啊 熱門一個Po都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> copy呢段嘢幫手同我洗板<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CG0pAnJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCG0pAnJ.jpg&h=1f177d7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3aac7e75bac038bac5794ae1d5c2d595be0beb80","tid":1801911,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:40:07.000Z","msg":"狗查狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈的障礙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"57a38c491794363d053c2ce7b55cc2ce37415c9a","tid":1801911,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:49:49.000Z","msg":"德國聯署有三份 <span style=\"color: red;\">呢家仲有一份未達標</span><br />\n而且差好遠呀 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">6xxx/50000</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=e4d44973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a>"}]}